WooCommerce Account Page Builder

With My Account Page Builder for WooCommerce, you can add or remove custom sections from the My Account Page and alter the WooCommerce parts that come with it. These sections can contain any type of material, including words, photographs, videos, downloadable files, discount codes, and more.
